"                    -H_{ij}(-\\delta Q_k+\\delta Q_l) + H_{ij}(-\\delta Q_k+\\delta Q_l)}\n"
"                    {4\\delta Q_k \\delta Q_l}"
msgstr "k_{ijkl} = \\frac{H_{ij}(+\\delta Q_k+\\delta Q_l) - H_{ij}(+\\delta Q_k-\\delta Q_l)\n"
